{"tid":1150884,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎講下你最憎食d咩","createTime":"2019-05-12T07:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T08:34:23.000Z","uid":59676,"like":5,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"4aeadb492b24ae834accd55846d363820e3a5772","tid":1150884,"uid":59676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:34:58.000Z","msg":"1. 田雞<br />\n是咁的, 以前屋企人整過一次俾我食, 食完就病撚左, 搞到我又痾又嘔。 有時都諗唔明點解會有人鐘意食, 明明隻野咁撚樣衰, 見到都唔開胃啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.qm120.com/image/20181019/20181019100409_79262.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.qm120.com%2Fimage%2F20181019%2F20181019100409_79262.jpg&h=8b56fcec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 紅蘿蔔 <br />\n紅蘿蔔呢樣野無論點整/煮/生食都好，我成日形住好勁既草腥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 真係狗都唔屌."},{"pid":"1a00b1eefa89c4595b10497a071a5788eb0e676d","tid":1150884,"uid":199162,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:36:27.000Z","msg":"老了 食嘢為營養 已經唔在意好唔好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea219bc9292d34e17aa4087baa298645579272c","tid":1150884,"uid":59676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a00b1eefa89c4595b10497a071a5788eb0e676d","tid":1150884,"uid":199162,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:36:27.000Z","msg":"老了 食嘢為營養 已經唔在意好唔好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"但都唔係咩都放入口架"},{"pid":"13a1a125c